rizontal cursor position\nchar_seq - the character or character sequence\n\nFor width:\n\\- Regular characters occupy one cell\n\\- Non-printable characters and escape sequences occupy zero cells\n\\- Full width characters occupy two cells\n\n```pycon\n>>> text_width = lambda s: sum(width for ((_, width), _) in measure(s))\n>>> text_width(\"hello, world\")\n12\n>>> text_width(f\"hello, {ansi_green}world{reset}\")\n[12]\n>>> measure_text(\"hello, \uff57\uff4f\uff52\uff4c\uff44\")\n[17]\n>>> measure_text(f\"hello, {ansi_green}\uff57\uff4f\uff52\uff4c\uff44{reset}\")\n[17]\n>>> measure_text(\"hello\\nworld\")\n```\n"]}], "variables": [{"name": "pansi.text._PADDED_SEGMENT_BREAK", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pansi.text._TWO_OR_MORE_SPACES", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pansi.text._COLOR_FUNCTION", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pansi.text._TEXT_TO_SUBSCRIPT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pansi.text._TEXT_TO_SUPERSCRIPT", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pansi.text.CGA_PALETTE", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "pansi.text.Text", "bases": ["Sequence"], "methods": [{"name": "pansi.text.Text.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "text", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "tab_size", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "encoding", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "errors", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pansi.text.Text.tab_size", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pansi.text.Text.measurements", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "pansi.text.Text.__repr__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "retur